<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2>Welcome to <%= @course.title %></h2>

      <p>Dear <%= @user.full_name %>,</p>

      <p>Welcome! You have successfully enrolled in the course "<%= @course.title %>".</p>

      <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <h3>Enrollment Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Course:</strong> <%= @course.title %></p>
        <p><strong>Instructor:</strong> <%= @course.instructor&.full_name %></p>
        <% if @batch %>
          <p><strong>Batch:</strong> <%= @batch.title %></p>
          <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> <%= @batch.start_date&.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
        <% end %>
        <p><strong>Enrollment Date:</strong> <%= @enrollment.enrolled_at&.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
      </div>

      <p>You can now access your course materials and start learning. Track your progress and complete assignments to earn certificates.</p>

      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to your instructor or our support team.</p>

      <p>Happy learning!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The LMS Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>